</div>

<h2>Project Description</h2>
<p><strong>Automation:</strong> Designed a shell script to automate the sequential restart of worker nodes, minimizing downtime and manual intervention.</p>
<p><strong>Scheduling:</strong> The script was scheduled to execute during low-usage windows, optimizing cluster availability and performance.</p>
<p><strong>Integration:</strong> Solution was deployed on Linux-based HD Insight clusters, leveraging built-in scheduling tools for reliability.</p>

